Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說過世間萬物都有著靈魂 這樣的說法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼 只要被珍惜的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習神仙愛心蛋 就會從中誕生哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是秘密事項喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大危機！想出卻出不來的莎莎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼哇～ 睡的真香！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦～ 早安啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4 愛心蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡過頭了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 糟糕了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！心彩快起床！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上學要遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(444,647)}起床啊！心彩！遲到了 遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,708)}太陽閃閃發光的早上了 快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！醒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,週日還想睡個懶覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子她媽？孩子她媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯... 哦 早安 心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 有見到媽媽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是出門去哪兒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 在書房的書架上放著水煮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 為什麼要把水煮蛋放在那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 心彩的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 覺得肚子餓就做了 結果忘記不知道放到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 原來放在那裡了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是成長期～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗！ 美蘿莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 急急忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 在書房裡的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是愛心蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 用勁敲開吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敲不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問～ 有在裡面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是愛心蛋的契約者 叫做心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的話 出來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚嗚...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好想出來啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 出不來啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳咳 剛才略有失態 不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請見諒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先做一下自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是書本的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自又大又厚的百科全書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎 說個不停的主 御言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我莎莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大... 又大又厚的莎莎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 為什麼莎莎出不來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來話長 我盡量說的簡潔一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗耳恭聽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨夜 我作為愛心蛋誕生的那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所寄宿的書被什麼人給撕掉了一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果 就只有蛋成型了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書被撕掉了 好可憐啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 愛心蛋是要被珍惜的使用 才會誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把被撕掉的書頁補好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 我就能從蛋裡出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必幫助我 心彩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到書頁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對會找到 幫你從蛋裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗 美蘿莉 也會一起幫忙的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝諸位的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份恩情 我會銘記一生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪本是莎莎的書？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是『世界大百科全書』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被撕掉的是其中的第三冊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大好厚的書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這書很有意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 記載了各種各樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從浩瀚無垠的宇宙 到烤博餅的做法 無所不含
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是十分偉大的百科全書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不知道的東西可以通過網絡搜索的當下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四葉家的家人 依然很重視直接查閱書籍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別喜歡使用這套百科
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！書頁沒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此 為什麼把『SHI』這頁給撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是個不解之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼解開這個謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能知道是誰撕掉的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就開始做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 先吃過早飯 慢慢想這個問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是 餓著肚子是沒法上陣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖這麼說 但是我吃不了東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大口大口的吃個飽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是這麼說 就越在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是小誠的不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 老師說的太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 姐姐怎麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同 同感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡那個女孩子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 幫我拿一下巧克力醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 孩子他爹 加太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能光吃甜食 對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸被媽媽火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？笑聲似乎多了幾個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哈哈哈 嗚呼呼呼 呀哈哈哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯 錯覺吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 說起來 媽媽剛才去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了洗衣店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 很中意的裙子上被淋到醬油了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 一早就去店裡做祛漬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎題解開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 搞清楚了 搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎題什麼 心彩真是誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是因為 媽媽在週日早上一個人出門 實在太少見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈～ 我吃飽了 多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 謎題解開了 這怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 為什麼書頁被撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 是誰撕的 都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是媽媽嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的正是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醬油淋到了中意的裙子上的媽媽 手忙腳亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在百科查找祛漬的方法時候 把書頁給撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(880,650)}【拔】
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『SHI』那頁被撕 是因為記載了祛漬的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 在去洗衣店的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了隱瞞把書弄破了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無疑是把書頁丟垃圾桶了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎腦子真好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得媽媽是不會這麼做的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！ 絕對是那樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了證明我的推理是完美無瑕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去外面的垃圾桶找找就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 心彩小姐 即刻出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的街上沒有垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了！ 那裡肯定有！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～... 在這裡翻箱倒桶的 感覺好羞恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再羞恥也要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩好可憐啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了！這裡就由我使用魔法...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這些的話 就沒人能認出是心彩了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害！難得成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 心彩快穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯... 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就用這件還有這件以及這件！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚～ 沒有啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有 沒有啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 怎麼感覺更是醒目了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我是守護小鎮乾淨的假面衛（生）士！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正與這個危險的垃圾桶戰鬥中～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 是四葉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一之瀨同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日 日安... 啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 四葉挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呢嘻嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學在練足球？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就有場重要的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回見！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 掉東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了 四葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了 四葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶～ 心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 都忘了！我這COSPLAY啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎題又解開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(965,650)}【】
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『SHI』的那頁被撕 因為記載了怎麼帥氣的射門的方法！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學肯定在練習時打翻了垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在裡面發現了媽媽丟掉的書頁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無疑是想實踐一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何 都要把書頁給拿回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩小姐 快去追一之瀨同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～ 看樣子是很難拿回來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 心彩小姐 有在聽嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脫外套了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 有機可趁！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 從那外套裡拿書頁 也太引人注目了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時機 就要靠愛心蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小體積的話 就不會被發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的對 拜託了 塗塗 美蘿莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再高一點～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的說～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美蘿莉小姐～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗 美蘿莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗 在哪～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡 心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掛在樹枝上得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 兩人都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就來救你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 嚇死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶 胡蘿蔔 洋蔥 土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs30}福神漬：以七種材料醃製的醬菜，取七福神之名。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛肉 八寶菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎題再次解開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨家今晚吃咖喱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定 是幫媽媽跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那麼拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一之瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個掉在那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？ 又掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了 四葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學 向我道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩小姐！書頁要怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩小姐 太過分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉 會好好去找的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊... 一直以來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都很想見一見珍惜著我的四葉家人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這已經是無法實現的夢想了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎 我也想見到莎莎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會找到書頁的 別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對會做到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是！我也會拚命去找的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到前 決不放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝了 諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請 多多幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～... 嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被撕掉的書頁～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著 找找看排水溝吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩小姐 已經足夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位這麼拚命的去找 已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便沒能真正的誕生 我還是相當的幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放棄啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 都一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了！家裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒找過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會在家裡找到哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次謎題是真的解開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的犯人就是爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(791,650)}【】
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『SHI』的那項 記載著糖漿的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸喜歡甜食...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 吃太多的話 又會惹媽媽不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無疑是只能偷偷摸摸的自己做！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 心彩小姐 趕快回家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯... 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 心彩 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 零分...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 莫非這個是百科全書？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 清掃小誠的房間時 吸塵器從地毯裡吸出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 連百科的書頁也一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為 昨天夜裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去拿回藏起來的考卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 書突然發光 嚇了一跳 於是就...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書會發光？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能有那種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是用眼過度了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小誠遊戲玩太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時不許玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！？怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再藏試卷 好好的學習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把這書頁完整的補好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了 還要對書道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次介紹 我是書本的神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次 為了幫我 做了種種努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我簽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始 你就是愛心蛋之家的同伴了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多關照～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡 有多久沒有清掃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？每天都有啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？灰塵都像山一樣積起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個角角落落都要好好的清掃乾淨！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 現在就開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話 愛心蛋之家就像個垃圾場了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗先生 腰要用力！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用力的話 地板是不會閃閃發光的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美蘿莉小姐也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要細心去擦 玻璃才會通透！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼莎莎光說不練！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我弄髒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 有空抱怨給我把手動起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～ 但是這塊黑漬擦都擦不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有辦法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點亮吧 莎莎塾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候 要用橙皮來擦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙皮有能把像是魔術筆一類 油性物質溶解的效果！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 塗塗先生 用你的力量變出橙子吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我弄出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 出不來了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又被關起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來的話太煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我出去～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的愛心蛋占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運蛋是哪個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選到我的人 好運喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有新的愛心蛋來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是笑笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.74,0:24:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是電視機之神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講的段子無人能及
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.04,0:24:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在一起的話 肯定會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 塗塗要與笑笑決鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.44,0:24:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且輸掉的要離開家？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.70,0:24:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.82,0:24:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞笑神仙？笑笑是也！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,